aiSectionHeader.tagline: 👋 we have launched voz-ai infra for developers
aiSectionHeader.subTitle: Ai identity handles voz calls, whatsapp, and texts on your behalf, humanly. it understands context, remove clutter, takes action, and keep tabs on everything to give you, your freedom back.
aiHowItWorks.sectionSubTitle: From calls to clarity in simple steps
aiHowItWorks.title1: Crear an ai identity with a unique teléfono número.
aiHowItWorks.desc1: Anyone can llamada or whatsapp your ai identity for personal and professional conversations. it handles the llamada and patches you in if needed.
aiHowItWorks.title2: Offload noise, focus on things that matter
aiHowItWorks.desc2: Streamline your communication as ai identity filters excessive information. cortar through cluttered calls and messages with smart automatización.
aiHowItWorks.title3: Stay informed with real-hora insights and smart context tracking
aiHowItWorks.desc3: Never lose track of a conversación. your ai identity provides context, summaries, and key insights — even months later.
aiHowItWorks.title4: Execute tasks faster with smart workflows
aiHowItWorks.desc4: From scheduling meetings to updating tools, your ai connects with what you already use and automates actions directly from conversations.
aiHero.subHeading: Unpod connects with existing communication channels, data, tools. it streamlines conversations and executes actions on your behalf.
aiCta.title: Ready to transform your communication?
aiCta.description: Join thousands of businesses and individuals who trust our ai voz identities to handle their most important conversations.
aiCta.note: No credit card required • free 14-day trial • cancelar anytime
sipSectionHeader.heading: For voz ai
sipSectionHeader.subTitle: Connect your sip/telephony providers directly to voz ai infrastructure. one platform, endless possibilities for developers building the future of communication.
sipLightning.heading: Integración in < 5 mins
sipLightning.description: While our competitors can take days or weeks to get you up and running, voicebridge gets you integrated and making calls in under 5 mins. we have streamlined the entire process with our developer-primero API and comprehensive sdks, making integración incredibly simple for everyone.
sipPlatforms.heading: Connect with
sipPlatforms.subHeading: Seamlessly integrate with the platforms you already trust. our unified API connects you to the best-in-class voz and communication infrastructure.
sipVoiceBridge.heading: Why unpod.dev?
sipVoiceBridge.subHeading: We’ve built the voz ai puente we wanted to use, focused on creating the best developer experience. and if you give us a try, we’re sure you’ll agree.
sipVoiceBridge.feature1.title: Instant setup
sipVoiceBridge.feature1.desc: Get your sip-voz ai puente running in under 5 minutes, while competitors require hours of complex configuración and setup.
sipVoiceBridge.feature2.title: Developer-primero platform
sipVoiceBridge.feature2.desc: Our platform is designed to be intuitive and easy to work with, making voz ai integración a breeze with multiple platforms.
sipVoiceBridge.feature3.title: Multi-provider support
sipVoiceBridge.feature3.desc: Connect with vapi, livekit, diariamente, and more voz ai providers through a single unified interface, with no vendor lock-in.
sipVoiceBridge.feature4.title: Global edge network
sipVoiceBridge.feature4.desc: Automatically route calls through our worldwide infrastructure for optimal latency and llamada quality in 150+ countries.
sipVoiceBridge.feature5.title: Enterprise security
sipVoiceBridge.feature5.desc: Built-in compliance with hipaa, iso-27001, and telecom regulations, ensuring your voz data is always protected.
sipVoiceBridge.feature6.title: Real-hora analytics
sipVoiceBridge.feature6.desc: Monitor llamada quality, latency, and ai performance with detailed analytics and alerts to optimize your voz applications.
sipInnovation.description: Stop spending months building telecom infrastructure. our platform handles the complexity so you can focus on creating amazing voz experiences for your users.
sipInnovation.check1: Reduce development hora by 80% with pre-built integrations
sipInnovation.check2: Scale from 10 to 10m+ concurrent calls seamlessly
sipInnovation.check4: Pay-as-you-scale pricing with no upfront costs
